d. The 9 rows (versions 0–8) match what the CLI creates during normal `login`. Without them, the binary may attempt to re-migrate and fail.\\n- **Token refresh is automatic**: Only the initial `refresh_token` + `device-registration` need to be seeded. `kiro-cli-chat` handles refreshing the `access_token` using the OAuth client credentials from `device-registration`.\\n`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`\\n\\n**Next steps for you:**\\n1. Add the `KIRO_DEVICE_REG` secret to GitHub (extract with: `sqlite3 ~/Library/Application\\\\ Support/kiro-cli/data.sqlite3 \\\"SELECT value FROM auth_kv WHERE key='kirocli:odic:device-registration';\\\"`)\\n2. Update the `KIRO_AUTH_TOKEN` secret to contain the token row value (extract with: `sqlite3 ~/Library/Application\\\\ Support/kiro-cli/data.sqlite3 \\\"SELECT value FROM auth_kv WHERE key='kirocli:odic:token';\\\"`)\\n3. Push and run `e2e-isolated` with `agent=kiro` to verify\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1608,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":37691,\"output_tokens\":651,\"server_tool_use\":{\"web_search_requests\":0,\"web_fetch_requests\":0},\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":1608,\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0},\"inference_geo\":\"\",\"iterations\":[],\"speed\":\"standard\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYkhwv1oHpsVLfMvMLcLh\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"79c14f0f-9240-4aa1-b96b-8f23897adfb6\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-05T22:16:58.993Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"79c14f0f-9240-4aa1-b96b-8f23897adfb6\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alisha/Projects/wt/kiro-oneshot\",\"sessionId\":\"f4ab6660-ba4d-4488-ba34-43574ff63fd2\",\"version\":\"2.1.69\",\"gitBranch\":\"alisha/kiro-oneshot\",\"slug\":\"toasty-stargazing-mountain\",\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"type\":\"hook_progress\",\"hookEvent\":\"Stop\",\"hookName\":\"Stop\",\"command\":\"go run ${CLAUDE_PROJECT_DI